    "permit_type": "Plumbing PermitOne or Two Family Dwelling/StructureAddition/Alteration/Replacement",
    "work_description": "DRAIN WATER HEATER and reset on concrete blocks and reset and restrap. install new 3/4\"cold shut off valve to heater. install new washing machine all box and run water heater relief line into wall box. Install new 1\" stop and waste valve on water line where it enters basement and strap line to wall. Replace old washing machine 1 1/2\" abs line with new 2' line and install new washing machine wall box . Replace broken bathtub waste and overflow drain. Seperate tub drain and basin drain and run new 2\" abs line into 4\" cast iron stack with 4x4x2\" no-hub wye and test tee and test drain for tub drain. Expose all water connections where owner ran new piping without permits, change connection any connections thar are not proper. OPEN basement ceiling drywall to expose all connections for inspections. Hang dishwasher drain hose to counter top under Kitchen sink.",
